Embrace the unwavering elegance of Zhongli, the Geo Archon from Genshin Impact, and transform your browser into a realm of stone and legacy! 🗿🌟

Step into the timeless wisdom and grandeur of Zhongli every time you open a new tab. Known for his unshakable presence and unmatched knowledge, Zhongli brings his calm and majestic aura to your Chrome, offering an immersive and serene browsing experience. Whether you admire his power over Geo or his refined demeanor, this live wallpaper is perfect for fans of Teyvat's beloved Archon.

Key Features
🗿 Zhongli Animation: Stunning visuals of Zhongli, showcasing his commanding aura and mastery over Geo.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Effortlessly search the web while basking in Zhongli’s calming energy.
🕒 Clock & Date: A stylish time display harmonizing with Zhongli’s elegant theme.
🌐 Customizable Shortcuts: Tailor your tab with addable and removable shortcuts.
🔗 Manage Extensions: "Remove Extension" and "More Extensions" options are easily accessible in the bottom-left corner.
Bring the timeless power of Zhongli into your everyday browsing and let his presence remind you of strength, wisdom, and balance. This live wallpaper is a must-have for Genshin Impact fans who cherish the elegance of the Geo Archon.
